				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A player reacts to getting splattered in blood and guts when they are standing below the corpse chute of the Colony Cleansing Room, when it is opened up. On the first time, a corpse will come falling out, but afterwards the chute simply serves as a blood shower at the press of the button."
				}
